Project: MessageGPT

Original Creator
----------------
Aditya

Project Description
-------------------
MessageGPT is an AI-powered study and productivity platform.
It includes features such as AI chat, website generation,
mind map generation, diagrams, and other educational tools.

Development Timeline
--------------------
